properties.name: EXCEL_FORMATTED_TABLE
properties.description: Use formatting from the original spreadsheet.

properties.name: EXCEL_UNFORMATTED_TABLE
properties.description: Convert the spreadsheet to an unformatted table.

properties.name: EXCEL_UNFORMATTED_TABBED_TEXT

properties.name: EXCEL_FORMAT_ONLY_ONCE
properties.description: Converts the spreadsheet to a table that is formatted only on initial import but not on update.
